<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201120/30c2995b6fcb4df2a10279d760bccdfe.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20201120/5c99d57c0ca54d0192e5987b52c8eb5d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">破旧古朴的乡村变为风景优美的村落</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">充满现代文明气息</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">又保持古老村落的文化底蕴</p>
